非最好需改良 西方政制想改都改不了<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英出席論壇，他辭詞時說，西方的選票制度不能說是最好的，亦不相信目前國家的政治制度已是最好，認為在未來日子，仍需要不斷改良。<br />\n<br />\n不過梁振英認為，中國的政制好處在於如果想改可以改，但西方的政治制度已經到了，想改都改不了的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />689都支持想改可以改國家制度<br />\n真心說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a0b944e480d7b7bb4d3047f93f8dab58494bb4","tid":1590832,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"改做更獨裁？"},{"pid":"05869b2f42bccbf7b91516c26ff3eca5aae44fc4","tid":1590832,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:21:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aa4af47ca09fe0ea677d0ee8f87f584a800af01","tid":1590832,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a0b944e480d7b7bb4d3047f93f8dab58494bb4","tid":1590832,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"改做更獨裁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/40Lhwjp3UDg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F40Lhwjp3UDg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=386b44cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81c36c675b81d30f1efffc4b834c7b93bbb6575e","tid":1590832,"uid":67454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"你攞緊0分咪有可改進空間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地就快滿分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cc60d6915797fe60d1a47da3b3c56f17280b47","tid":1590832,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abec5dcda9478b867fb1fc349de5a39a1707e361","tid":1590832,"uid":34140,"lik